00:06:04.139 --> 00:06:08.869
marrow, cow’s head, and, of course, plenty of raw liver.

00:06:10.228 --> 00:06:14.118
His philosophy is that humans should eat the whole animal,

00:06:14.438 --> 00:06:19.728
nose-to-tail, horns-to-hooves, and that is what he seems to eat.

00:06:20.708 --> 00:06:23.518
Now, you might think, good on him, if you are going to

00:06:23.518 --> 00:06:25.768
eat meat then you should eat every part of an animal.

00:06:26.588 --> 00:06:32.538
Or you might think, “eugh”, I don’t like the idea of eating raw, cold bull testicles.

00:06:34.038 --> 00:06:36.728
Liver King’s view is certainly the former.

00:06:37.558 --> 00:06:42.898
He believes, and says in practically every interview he does, that processed foods

00:06:43.108 --> 00:06:48.278
are one of the worst things about the modern world, and that by cutting these

00:06:48.298 --> 00:06:54.438
out entirely, by returning to an ancestral diet, our bodies will be healthier.

00:06:55.868 --> 00:06:58.498
You might say, sure, he does have a point.

00:06:59.078 --> 00:07:05.138
The health dangers of processed foods, especially super-processed foods, are well documented.

00:07:05.898 --> 00:07:10.898
And let’s remember that Liver King is American, his audience is mainly

00:07:10.898 --> 00:07:16.358
American, and the US is the capital of super processed, unhealthy food.

00:07:17.188 --> 00:07:21.699
So, it’s hardly surprising that this message resonated with his audience.

