ask his wife, his so-called “Liver Queen”, who could cut it with a machete, a large hunting knife.

00:09:04.231 --> 00:09:09.721
So, why did he do all of this, what turned Brian Johson into Liver King?

00:09:10.691 --> 00:09:14.251
If you listen to any of his interviews, he would talk about the fact that

00:09:14.261 --> 00:09:19.201
he developed this ancestral lifestyle as a way of surviving after his

00:09:19.201 --> 00:09:23.601
kids were ill, after one had allergic reactions to “the modern world”.

00:09:25.201 --> 00:09:30.055
He realised, so he said, that by feeding his children the traditional

00:09:30.075 --> 00:09:34.725
American diet he was, and I’m quoting directly, killing them.

00:09:35.665 --> 00:09:39.755
His kids couldn’t breathe, they turned blue, and the only

00:09:39.755 --> 00:09:43.795
way to save them was by returning to the diet of a caveman.

00:09:45.005 --> 00:09:47.265
