00:09:47.635 --> 00:09:51.715
Everyone wants to do the right thing for their kids, Liver King

00:09:51.725 --> 00:09:56.675
looked happy and healthy, and he soon gathered millions of followers.

00:09:57.945 --> 00:10:02.365
TikTok was his main channel, with almost 5 million followers at the

00:10:02.365 --> 00:10:06.765
time of recording, and Instagram came shortly after, with 2 million.

00:10:07.505 --> 00:10:09.915
He was getting very popular indeed.

00:10:11.265 --> 00:10:15.485
Clearly, for some people it was all a bit of fun, watching this

00:10:15.695 --> 00:10:19.955
slightly strange man eating unusual things and lifting large weights.

00:10:20.945 --> 00:10:25.025
But for plenty of people, it was a powerful message.

00:10:25.775 --> 00:10:31.025
What if they too could become happier and healthier by doing what Liver King did?

00:10:31.595 --> 00:10:35.735
Why not give this ancestral living thing a shot, why not give it a try?

00:10:37.165 --> 00:10:40.655
Liver King knew, of course, that simply switching to

00:10:40.665 --> 00:10:44.025
ancestral living isn’t a feasible option for most people.

00:10:44.785 --> 00:10:48.695
You can’t just decide, ok, I’m going to eat fresh bull testicles

00:10:48.725 --> 00:10:53.065
every day from a bull I’ve just killed, and my boss will probably be

00:10:53.065 --> 00:10:57.465
a bit cross if I turn up topless to work every day and stop shaving.

00:10:58.275 --> 00:11:02.515
But no problem, Liver King had a solution.

00:11:03.835 --> 00:11:09.935
If you go to liverking.com, you will find all manner of supplements and snack bars,

00:11:10.155 --> 00:11:14.925
vetted by Liver King himself, that allow you to get all of the nutrition you need.

00:11:16.185 --> 00:11:19.185
And, as you might imagine, it’s not cheap.

00:11:20.095 --> 00:11:23.825
A bag of protein supplements would set you back $64,

00:11:24.265 --> 00:11:29.095
and a case of 12 Liver King bars costs a mere $42.

00:11:29.945 --> 00:11:35.225
And both were, I quote, “guaranteed to help you dominate your environment”.

00:11:36.555 --> 00:11:40.105
Now, it’s not clear quite how much money Liver King made

00:11:40.205 --> 00:11:45.225
selling these, but he claimed more than $100 million per year.

00:11:46.675 --> 00:11:52.165
Whatever the number, it's certainly enough to fund a pretty lavish lifestyle, a private

00:11:52.165 --> 00:11:58.085
chef, trips around the world, and a seemingly constant camera crew to film his every move.

00:11:59.095 --> 00:12:03.775
The problem was, was he really practising what he preached?

00:12:04.745 --> 00:12:09.555
Yes, there were plenty of videos of him taking ice baths, wandering around with

00:12:09.555 --> 00:12:15.115
no shoes and shirts, and, lest I forget, gulping down uncooked bull testicles.

00:12:15.865 --> 00:12:20.355
But something seemed off, something seemed unlikely.

00:12:21.345 --> 00:12:28.305
His muscles were so big, so large, could this really all come down to his lifestyle choice?

00:12:28.835 --> 00:12:33.245
Could you too become like him just by following his lifestyle?

00:12:34.565 --> 00:12:38.795
Well, as you have probably guessed given this is part of a series on

00:12:38.795 --> 00:12:42.975
The Great American Con Artist, there was something off with Liver King.

00:12:44.295 --> 00:12:49.425
Many people had claimed that he was on steroids, most famously the podcaster Joe

00:12:49.445 --> 00:12:55.745
Rogan, who said, and I’m quoting directly, “that guy has an assfull of steroids”.

00:12:57.115 --> 00:13:02.805
As a result, as Liver King toured the world, going on podcasts and giving interviews,

00:13:03.075 --> 00:13:08.025
he was constantly asked about this, asked flat out, “do you take steroids?”

00:13:09.275 --> 00:13:12.215
And again and again, he denied this.

00:13:13.215 --> 00:13:18.365
In fact, he embraced it, he seemed to loved being asked about his steroid

00:13:18.365 --> 00:13:22.985
use, because it gave him an opportunity to, yet again, promote his

00:13:22.985 --> 00:13:27.285
ancestral lifestyle, and his extensive line of products that you could buy.

00:13:28.385 --> 00:13:32.145
Every denial was another opportunity to promote his

00:13:32.315 --> 00:13:35.745
alternative way, to get more customers, to make more money.

00:13:37.145 --> 00:13:41.648
The problem was, at the end of 2022, fewer than  18 months

00:13:41.828 --> 00:13:46.118
after his social media took off, some private emails leaked.

00:13:47.318 --> 00:13:50.088
And these emails were explosive.

00:13:50.958 --> 00:13:56.188
It turned out that Liver King was putting something non-ancestral into his body.

00:13:57.248 --> 00:14:03.458
Yes, he was on large quantities of steroids, spending around $11,000

00:14:03.508 --> 00:14:08.088
every month on a wide variety of different drugs to build his muscles.

00:14:09.678 --> 00:14:15.148
This body he had, that he claimed was only possible because of the strict ancestral

00:14:15.148 --> 00:14:20.298
lifestyle that he followed, was in fact made possible by large amounts of drugs.

00:14:21.238 --> 00:14:27.688
He had lied, and it wasn’t just a small lie about accidentally eating a chocolate bar or a hot dog.

00:14:28.228 --> 00:14:32.448
His entire brand, his entire message, everything he

00:14:32.448 --> 00:14:35.648
stood for, was about being natural and ancestral.

00:14:36.488 --> 00:14:40.908
And there he was, pumping his body full of steroids every day.

00:14:41.728 --> 00:14:47.708
The emails were conclusive, they were between him and a private doctor, there was no way he

00:14:47.708 --> 00:14:53.628
could deny them, and he was forced to issue a public apology to his millions of followers.

00:14:54.988 --> 00:15:00.538
Some of whom vowed to never buy anything from him again, others were more forgiving.

00:15:01.798 --> 00:15:07.238
And of course, Liver King being Liver King, he also took the opportunity to go on a

00:15:07.308 --> 00:15:12.958
PR blitz, a tour of different shows and podcasts, where he talked about his steroid

00:15:12.958 --> 00:15:18.788
use but again, portrayed himself as a victim, someone who only wanted to promote

00:15:18.808 --> 00:15:24.508
this amazing ancestral lifestyle, and someone who got caught up in his own success.

00:15:25.724 --> 00:15:30.754
Since all of this, which came out in December of 2022, he has

00:15:30.754 --> 00:15:35.874
pledged to be Liver King 2.0, Liver King without steroids.

00:15:37.044 --> 00:15:41.494
And if you go to his social media channels, you can still find him doing

00:15:41.494 --> 00:15:46.224
exactly the same stuff: eating liver, heart and testicles, lifting heavy

00:15:46.224 --> 00:15:51.450
weights, throwing axes at trees, and of course promoting his supplement brands.

00:15:52.824 --> 00:15:58.294
To someone who didn’t know about the steroid revelations, nothing has changed, and no

00:15:58.294 --> 00:16:03.634
doubt he is still selling tens of millions of dollars of Liver King products every month.

00:16:05.034 --> 00:16:09.504
Now, why was Liver King’s message so appealing to so many people?

00:16:10.464 --> 00:16:13.894
Firstly, it was unique, it was strange.

00:16:14.534 --> 00:16:18.294
After all, if you are scrolling through social media and you see a

00:16:18.304 --> 00:16:23.394
video of someone holding a raw cow’s liver, you probably stop and watch.

00:16:24.984 --> 00:16:27.594
Secondly, it seemed obvious.

00:16:28.064 --> 00:16:32.804
We know that highly processed foods can be bad for us, and a raw

00:16:32.814 --> 00:16:37.144
bull’s testicle is the polar opposite of a highly processed hot dog.

00:16:38.294 --> 00:16:40.114
Thirdly, it was simple.

00:16:40.714 --> 00:16:44.144
Eat, sleep, connect with nature, do exercise.

00:16:44.634 --> 00:16:48.274
These are all easy things to do, we kind of already know that

00:16:48.274 --> 00:16:51.664
they’re good for us, and it’s an easy message to understand.

00:16:53.034 --> 00:16:57.034
In fact, even disregarding the steroid revelations, much

00:16:57.034 --> 00:17:00.264
of what Liver King was preaching was good, common sense.

00:17:01.604 --> 00:17:05.414
Fourth, Liver King had a powerful personal message.

00:17:05.724 --> 00:17:10.834
He said that he did this to save his kids, and anyone can connect with that.

00:17:12.084 --> 00:17:16.944
Now, given what we know about Liver King’s commitment to the truth, who knows whether

00:17:16.944 --> 00:17:22.354
this was a fabrication to sell more supplements, but to many it was a genuine message.

00:17:23.514 --> 00:17:27.634
And finally, Liver King was living proof of the results.

00:17:28.194 --> 00:17:31.474
You just needed to look at him to see what you could look like

00:17:31.474 --> 00:17:35.274
too if you followed his advice and bought his supplements.

00:17:36.244 --> 00:17:38.784
Except, of course…he wasn’t.

00:17:39.964 --> 00:17:43.994
There might have been some positive elements to Liver King’s message, but his

00:17:43.994 --> 00:17:50.174
entire brand of health and happiness was underpinned by something very un-ancestral.

00:17:51.414 --> 00:17:59.424
To quote Joe Rogan, he had an “assfull of steroids”, it was, after all, one big lie.

